org.apache.calcite.plan

类 TableAccessMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.plan.TableAccessMap

  • public class TableAccessMap
extends Object
    TableAccessMap represents the tables accessed by a query plan, with READ/WRITE information.
